<tr id="L342"><td><a href="#L342">342</a></td><td>ODO:  No, no. Odo'ital literally means the word 'nothing'. Even after it became clear that I was sentient, the Bajoran scientists kept calling me that. As a joke, they split it into two words like a Bajoran name, Odo Ital, which eventually got shortened.</td></tr>

<tr id="L343"><td><a href="#L343">343</a></td><td>KIRA:  To Odo.</td></tr>

